Accordingly, 30 CFR Parts 701, 773, 778, 840, and 843 are amended as set forth below:




PART 701_PERMANENT REGULATORY PROGRAM





1. The authority citation for part 701 continues to read as follows:








Authority:

 Pub. L. 9587 (30 U.S.C. 1201 

et seq.

), and Pub. L. 10034.





701.5 

[Amended]





2. Section 701.5 is amended by deleting the definition of ``Violation notice.''




